    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road with this dependable daily driver! This vehicle is in fair condition and offers a fantastic opportunity for someone looking for a reliable ride at a great value. While it shows some honest wear and tear from its journeys, it remains a solid performer that's ready to take you where you need to go while you add your own personal touches!",
