      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to an uncompromising showroom standard. This vehicle transcends the typical pre-owned inventory, offering a pristine aesthetic and mechanical integrity that mirrors its original delivery state. Every surface, from the flawless coachwork to the meticulously preserved cabin, reflects a history of elite stewardship. For the discerning professional who requires a vehicle indistinguishable from new, this offering represents an unparalleled acquisition opportunity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
